<subSubSection id="C33BAC836005FFA5FE2814B15F03FC66" pageId="37" pageNumber="37" type="reference_group">
<paragraph id="8B9EFF086005FFA5FE2814B15F03FC66" blockId="37.[189,1135,919,1012]" pageId="37" pageNumber="37">
Presl, Reliq. Haenk. 1 (4-5): 308. 1830. 
<emphasis id="B955231A6005FFA5FC1C14B15A46FC3D" bold="true" box="[972,1026,919,943]" pageId="37" pageNumber="37">Tipo</emphasis>
: México. Guerrero: Acapulco, 
<emphasis id="B955231A6005FFA5FE77149D5C03FC40" box="[423,583,954,978]" italics="true" pageId="37" pageNumber="37">T. Haenke s.n.</emphasis>
